N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 670.9 - Revisions

State Regulations

On a periodic basis the department shall review and
consider proposing amendments to this Part. Any amendments to this Part shall
be made in the same manner as its initial promulgation. Notes
